 Damon Albarn 透露他不想在 Blur 温布利演出的第二天晚上表演https://www.nme.com/news/music/damon-albarn-reveals-he-didnt-want-to-perform-during-the-second-night-of-blurs-wembley-shows-3618311?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=damon-albarn-透露他不想在模糊温布利演出的第二晚表演Surej SinghTue, 16 Apr 2024 04:37:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3618311 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Blur 的达蒙·阿尔本 (Damon Albarn)" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我正在寻找取消它的理由”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/damon-albarn-reveals-he-didnt-want-to-perform-during-the-second-night-of-blurs-wembley-shows-3618311">Damon Albarn 透露他不想在 Blur 温布利演出的第二天晚上表演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Blur 的达蒙·阿尔本 (Damon Albarn)" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Blur-Coachella-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/damon-albarn">达蒙·阿尔巴恩 (Damon Albarn)</a>透露，他不想在乐队去年的第二场温布利演出中表演。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/blur-live-in-london-wembley-setlist-photos-review-3466214">伦敦的 Blur 现场表演：体育场大小的纯粹、彻底的欢乐爆发</a></strong></li></ul><p>2022 年 11 月，Blur <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-2023-london-wembley-stadium-reunion-gig-buy-tickets-3348354">宣布将于 2023 年 7 月 8 日在温布利球场举行重聚演出</a>。由于需求旺盛，重聚演出变成了两人演出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-add-second-wembley-stadium-gig-due-to-phenomenal-demand-buy-tickets-3351758">不久后又宣布了第二场演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.rollingstone.co.uk/music/news/blur-say-wembley-stadium-comeback-was-their-best-ever-show-31469/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">据 Albarn 本人称，第二场演出于 7 月 9 日举行，后来成为他们“有史以来最好的”演出</a>。然而，7月9日的演出因阿尔巴恩不想演出而濒临取消。</p><p>阿尔巴恩 (Albarn) 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">科切拉 (Coachella</a> ) 开幕周末接受<em>KROQ</em>采访时透露了差点取消的消息，他分享道：“我从没想过自己会喜欢温布利。第一个晚上很棒，但第二天晚上，我不想再做一场演出了。我试图寻找取消它的理由。我坐在温布利公园的一家酒店里，就像旅行旅馆之类的，我看着这些人进来，我想，‘好吧，我不能取消这个’。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Blur 谈论他们重返科切拉音乐节" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hujkFC9VSnI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“实际上，这也许是那个时期你能梦想拥有的最好的演出。但这很奇怪，我真的不喜欢上台，然后我就上台了，这样做真是太好了。”</p><p>在采访的其他地方，Albarn 和 Alex James 谈到了 Blur <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-to-release-new-concert-film-and-documentary-on-2023-reunion-3585514">即将推出的纪录片，讲述了他们的重聚、温布利演出以及他们的复出专辑</a>《The Ballad Of Darren》。詹姆斯说道：“我们上次做任何事已经有八年了——即使我们真的分手了，也没有花那么长时间就走到了一起。因此，在职业生涯的这个阶段尝试创造新纪录，一开始可能会面临一定的危险。大多数乐队 30 年后甚至都不喜欢彼此，更不用说制作像样的唱片了。我想这其中有很多可责备的地方。我想如果你喜欢这个乐队，那是一个很好的乐队。我们在温布利拍摄了这些节目，我从没想过我们会超越 2009 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节。” </p><figure id="attachment_3466455" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3466455" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3466455" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/blur-wembley@2000x1270.jpg" alt="模糊" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/blur-wembley@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/blur-wembley@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/blur-wembley@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/blur-wembley@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/blur-wembley@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/blur-wembley@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3466455" class="wp-caption-text"> Blur 乐队的达蒙·阿尔本 (Damon Albarn) 和格雷厄姆·考克森 (Graham Coxon) 于 2023 年 7 月 8 日在英国伦敦温布利体育场演出。图片来源：吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>在与<em>KROQ</em>交谈之后，Blur 继续在 Coachella 音乐节上向平淡无奇的观众表演。演出期间，阿尔本<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/damon-albarn-tells-blurs-lackluster-coachella-crowd-youre-never-seeing-us-again-so-you-might-as-well-fucking-sing-it-3617844">在舞台上向冷漠的观众表演，同时表达了他的沮丧</a>。 “你可以做得比这更好，”他有一次对与会者说，周围安静的人群围观。当他仍然没有得到想要的回应时，主唱说：“你再也见不到我们了，所以你还不如他妈的唱这首歌。知道我在说什么吗？”</p><p>尽管主唱表示这将是观众最后一次看到这支传奇的英伦流行乐队，但乐队将于本周末（4 月 19 日至 21 日）返回科切拉山谷参加音乐节的第二个周末。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/damon-albarn-reveals-he-didnt-want-to-perform-during-the-second-night-of-blurs-wembley-shows-3618311">Damon Albarn 透露他不想在 Blur 温布利演出的第二天晚上表演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 表示，她在发行首张专辑之前就一直在计划“激进乐观” https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-says-shes-been-planning-for-radical-optimism-since-before-her-debut-album-3618307?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign= dua-lipa 说她从首张专辑开始就一直在计划激进的乐观主义Surej SinghTue, 16 Apr 2024 03:47:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3618307 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Dua Lipa 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手还表示她的新专辑比她以前的唱片“更成熟”</p><p> Dua Lipa 的帖子称，在她的首张专辑首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-says-shes-been-planning-for-radical-optimism-since-before-her-debut-album-3618307">之前，她就一直在计划“激进乐观”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Dua Lipa 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-favourite-thing-about-Glastonbury-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a>透露，在发行首张唱片之前，她就一直在为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-new-album-radical-optimism-announce-artwork-tracklist-preorder-3600718">即将发行的专辑《激进乐观》(Radical Optimism)</a>做准备。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/dua-lipa-houdini-track-review-lyrics-3534865">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 的《胡迪尼》暗示了一个受驯服黑斑羚影响的时代，你将不想逃离</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位“Don&#39;t Start Now”歌手在接受<a href="https://time.com/6965325/dua-lipa-interview-time100-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《时代》杂志</em></a>采访时谈到了“Radical Optimism”，该歌曲将于 5 月 3 日发行（<a href="https://dualipa.lnk.to/radicaloptimism" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。在与该出版物的交谈中，她透露她相信表现，并说：“表现对我来说是一件大事。我非常坚定地将事物投入到世界中的信念。潜意识里，你只是朝着他们努力。没有什么是太大的。”</p><p>这也体现在她即将发行的唱片上，她说她已经考虑了很长时间——确切地说，可以追溯到她 2017 年的首张同名专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3600733" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3600733" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3600733" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-press-pic_Credit-Tyrone-Lebon.jpg" alt="杜阿·利帕" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-press-pic_Credit-Tyrone-Lebon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-press-pic_Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-press-pic_Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-press-pic_Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-press-pic_Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DuaLipa-press-pic_Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3600733" class="wp-caption-text"> Dua Lipa 公布了她新专辑的详细信息 – 图片来源：Tyrone Lebon</figcaption></figure><p> “我记得当我制作第一张专辑时，我正在记下我的第三张专辑的内容，”利帕对<em>《时代》杂志</em>说。 “想想就很疯狂，但我记得我和我的密友兼 A&amp;R Joe [Kentish] 说过，‘也许第三张专辑，我可以和 [ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tame-impala">Tame Impala 的</a>] <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-parker">Kevin Parker</a>合作，’他说，‘好吧，别着急。 ，让我们迈出小步吧。”</p><p>利帕当时还认为，如果她的前两张唱片很受欢迎，那么“也许我值得与一位我如此钦佩和尊敬的艺术家共处一室。”</p><p> Dua Lipa 还表示，《激进乐观》将展示她的成长：“这张唱片整体上更加成熟。我绝对不再是我写第一张专辑时的那个人了。我已经进步并学到了很多……顺其自然，不认为有什么糟糕的事情或挫折。这需要大量的成长和了解自己，了解自己的价值，无论是在商业、爱情还是友谊方面。” </p><figure id="attachment_3577137" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3577137" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3577137" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa.-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon.jpg" alt="杜阿·利帕新闻图片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa.-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa.-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa.-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa.-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa.-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa.-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3577137" class="wp-caption-text">杜阿·利帕.信用蒂龙·勒邦</figcaption></figure><p>“我只是一个不同的人，所以这张唱片当然会有所不同，”她补充道。 “我有不同的想法、愿望、需求和观点。我对自己进行了 180 度大转变……此时此刻，我感觉自己是人生中最自信的时刻。”</p><p> Dua Lipa 最近发行了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-dua-lipa-dancey-new-single-illusion-3616686">专辑的第三首单曲“Illusion”</a> 。她于去年 11 月初发行了专辑中的第一首单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/dua-lipa-houdini-track-review-lyrics-3534865">《Houdini》</a> ，随后推出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-dua-lipas-empowering-new-single-training-season-3588357">《Training Season》</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-gives-training-season-live-debut-at-the-2024-grammys-3582190">于今年早些时候在格莱美颁奖典礼上首次亮相</a>。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">Lipa 确认将</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>一起成为 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的主角。据报道，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-reportedly-wants-to-use-glastonbury-2024-footage-for-upcoming-movie-3609581">准备拍摄她对沃西农场的访问，拍摄一部新的纪录片</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-announces-one-off-london-show-at-royal-albert-hall-buy-tickets-3608988">她还宣布今年秋天将在伦敦历史悠久的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅举办一场一次性音乐会</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-adds-european-headline-shows-to-summer-2024-radical-optimism-tour-3602852">于今年夏天举办一系列欧洲演出</a>。</p><p> Dua Lipa 的帖子称，在她的首张专辑首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-says-shes-been-planning-for-radical-optimism-since-before-her-debut-album-3618307">之前，她就一直在计划“激进乐观”</a> 。</p> ;
